official_title: To amend the Public Health Service Act to reauthorize and extend funding for community health centers.
short_title: Community Health Investment, Modernization, and Excellence Act of 2017

summary.text:
Community Health Investment, Modernization, and Excellence Act of 2017

This bill amends the Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act to extend through FY2022 and make appropriations for enhanced funding for the community health centers program.
